Overview 
The goal of the Workouts Product Management team is to develop effective, inspiring, and differentiated workouts on Tonal. As an intern on the team, you will be responsible for developing a deep understanding of user behavior and uncovering insights that will push the workout experience forward. 
 
 What You Will Do 
Identify product opportunities via market research, customer interviews, and analytics Conceptualize, scope, define, and drive projects through the product life cycle Communicate product details to senior management Track and measure the success of each release, and feed those learnings back into the roadmap 
Who You Are 
An upperclassmen, or graduate student pursuing a technical degree or MBA Excellent communication skills and interpersonal skills Self-starter, proactive, demonstrated self and team motivator with a bias for action Insatiable curiosity for understanding behavior and motivation, and defining experiences that exceed expectations Able to think both strategically and tactically An excellent problem-solver with extraordinary organizational and analytical abilities 
